Sales Life Cycle 		
=====================
-Inquiry 		** optional 
	 - inq is presales activities
	 *header details
		-inq. type
		-customer (sold to party)
		-bill to party
		-date
	 *details records 
		-item no.
		-product/material
		-qunatity
		-unit
		etc.
	
-Quotation 		** optional 
	*price
	*time line 
	*payment options ..
	
-Contract 		** optional 
	*documentation between buyer and saler
	*contract time line 

-Sales Order (SO)	** Mandatory 			
	 -Purchase Order (PO) - MM ** Mandatory

	*inq.
	*customer/sold to party
		/bill to party
	*item details
	  quantity
	  unit
	  date 
	  etc.		

-Receipt 
-Invoice 
-Billing 
	-Price Control
	-Inventory Management 


-Report 

 
